---
import ContentBlock from "../../components/astro/ContentBlock.astro";
import HeroBrick from "../../components/bricks/HeroBrick.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Type" hasHero="true" Theme="dark">
  <HeroBrick
    title="Type"
    text="<p>HENK uses Neue Haas Grotesk. Re-designed by Christian Schwartz, based on original Helvetica.</p>"
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596299786007-9974099be52b?q=80&w=3774&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
    url="#type-font"
    buttonText="Explore"
  />
  <!-- <p>HENK uses <a href='https://typenetwork.com/articles/neue-haas-grotesk-available-from-font-bureau'>Neue Haas Grotesk</a>. Re-designed by Christian Schwartz, based on original Helvetica.</p> -->
  <ContentBlock title="Font" id="type-font">
    <dl slot="content">
      <dt>Font:</dt>
      <dd><em>Haas Grot Text R Web</em></dd>
      <dt>Weights:</dt>
      <dd>Roman (400), Medium 500</dd>
      <dt>Styles:</dt>
      <dd>Regular, Italic</dd>
    </dl>
  </ContentBlock>
  <ContentBlock
    title="Typescale Roman"
    smallText="<p class='fs-x-small'>The HENK Typescale is founded upon a body text size of 16px, accompanied by a line-height of 24px (1.5 multiplier). Employing the <strong>Major Third as a modular scale</strong> (Scale 1.25), the Typescale encompasses a total of 8 font sizes.</p><p class='fs-x-small'>The concept of a modular scale in typography has deep historical roots and was eloquently explored by <strong>Robert Bringhurst</strong> in his seminal work, <em>'The Elements of Typographic Style.'</em></p><p class='fs-x-small'>In the realm of web design, Tim Brown has played a pivotal role in advancing this idea into practical application. His groundbreaking article marked the inception of utilizing modular scales in production, underscoring their relevance and impact in contemporary design practices. See his <a href='https://alistapart.com/article/more-meaningful-typography' target='_blank'>article that started it all</a>, or <a href='https://vimeo.com/17079380' target='_blank'>watch his event talk</a>.</p>"
  >
    <p
      class="fs-xxx-large baseline-8"
      slot="content"
      title="39px, line-height: 48px"
    >
      The quick brown fox<br /> jumps over the lazy dog
    </p>
    <p
      class="fs-xx-large baseline-8"
      slot="content"
      title="31px, line-height: 40px"
      style="background-position-y: 0px;"
    >
